Package gui.common

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ButtonBankListener
    ButtonBankListener is the callback interface for ButtonBankPanel.
    IController
    IController defines functionality that is supported by all controllers in the program.
    IView
    IView defines functionality that is supported by all views in the program.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ButtonBankPanel
    ButtonBankPanel can be used to easily create a horizontal bank of buttons, and to respond to the action events generated when the buttons are pressed.
    Controller
    Controller is a base class that provides common functionality required by all controllers in the program (i.e., all controller classes extend Controller).
    DialogBox
    Used to display modal dialog boxes.
    DialogView
    Base class for all views that are displayed in dialog boxes.
    GridBagConstraintsExt
    GridBagConstraintsExt is an extension of GridBagConstraints with an additional operation which makes it easy to reset the (x, y, width, height) properties in one shot.
    TableOperations
    TableOperations provides useful utility functions for operating on JTables.
    Tagable
    Tagable is the base class for all classes used to pass data into views.
    TreeOperations
    TreeOperations provides useful utility functions for operating on JTrees.
    View
    View is a base class that provides common functionality required by all views in the program (i.e., view classes extend View instead of JPanel).
    View.StringCellRenderer
    Table cell renderer used to draw table cells.
    View.TableHeaderRenderer
    Table cell renderer used to draw table headers.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FileFormat
    Enumeration defining all the output file formats supported by the program.
    SizeUnits
    Enumeration defining all the units of measurement (including weight, volume, and count) supported by the program.
